
<h3><a target="_out" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=icR14AGVNHM">WATCH: Video Tutorial: Make Bitcoin with OMG</a></h3>		
<p>
Each <b>thing</b> in the gallery has a <b>Tip Jar</b> that accepts Bitcoin (BTC).
</p>
<h4>How to make Bitcoin on OMG:</h4>
<ol>
<li>Download a Bitcoin wallet such as <a target="_out" href="https://electrum.org/#download">Electrum</a></li>
<li>Follow the setup instructions</li>
<li>Click on "Receive Money"</li>
<li>Copy the Bitcoin address</li>
Then:
<li>Paste the address in the <b>btc-address</b> on your <a href="/user.htm">User Page</a></li>
Or:
<li>Paste the address in the <b>btc-address</b> on the <b>song panel</b> in the editor</li>
</ol>
